---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Aviso de Privacidad">

	<!-- Hero (Flat Institutional) -->
	<section class="bg-yuc-green-dark text-white py-16 border-b-4 border-yuc-gold">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
			<span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded bg-yuc-gold/10 border border-yuc-gold/30 text-yuc-gold text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Gobierno del Estado de Yucatán</span>
			<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-white font-display">
				Aviso de Privacidad
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Protección y tratamiento de datos personales conforme a la normatividad aplicable del Estado de Yucatán.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded bg-white/10 text-xs text-slate-300 font-medium">
				Última actualización: 22 de mayo de 2026
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Main content -->
	<section class="bg-slate-50 py-12 sm:py-16">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

			<!-- Intro banner -->
			<div class="bg-yuc-green/5 border border-yuc-green/20 rounded p-6 mb-10 flex gap-4 items-start shadow-sm">
				<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-yuc-green text-white flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					El <strong class="text-slate-900 font-bold">Gobierno del Estado de Yucatán</strong>, con domicilio oficial en la <strong class="text-slate-900 font-bold">Calle 61 entre 60 y 62, Colonia Centro, C.P. 97000, Mérida, Yucatán</strong> (Palacio de Gobierno), es el responsable del tratamiento y protección de los datos personales que nos proporcione, los cuales serán manejados bajo los más estrictos estándares de seguridad y conforme a la normatividad vigente.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Secciones en layout de 2 columnas (escritorio) -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">

				<!-- Sec 1: Datos -->
				<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 font-display uppercase">Datos personales que se recaban</h2>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4 leading-relaxed">A través de este gestor web recolectaremos los siguientes datos personales:</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2.5">
						{["Nombre completo", "Clave Única de Registro de Población (CURP)", "Correo electrónico", "Número telefónico de contacto"].map(item => (
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-700">
								<span class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 border border-emerald-100">
									<svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
								</span>
								{item}
							</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Sec 3: Fundamento Legal -->
				<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-gold/10 text-yuc-gold-dark flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0012 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.971zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.971z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 font-display uppercase">Fundamento Legal</h2>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
						El tratamiento se realiza con fundamento en los artículos <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">16, 18, 21, 22, 25, 26 y 65</strong> de la Ley General de Protección de Datos Personales en Posesión de Sujetos Obligados, y en la <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">Ley de Protección de Datos Personales del Estado de Yucatán</strong>.
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>

			<!-- Sec 2: Finalidades (full width) -->
			<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-6 shadow-sm mb-6">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h3.75M9 15h3.375m0 0h3.375M9 15V9m12 3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 font-display uppercase">Finalidades del tratamiento</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
					<div class="bg-slate-50 rounded p-4 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 uppercase">Control y registro</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Verificar su identidad y gestionar su acceso como usuario registrado en la plataforma.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-slate-50 rounded p-4 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.857 17.082a23.848 23.848 0 005.454-1.31A8.967 8.967 0 0118 9.75v-.7V9A6 6 0 006 9v.75a8.967 8.967 0 01-2.312 6.022c1.733.64 3.56 1.085 5.455 1.31m5.714 0a24.255 24.255 0 01-5.714 0m5.714 0a3 3 0 11-5.714 0" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 uppercase">Fines informativos</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Notificarle sobre actualizaciones, resoluciones y comunicados oficiales vinculados a sus trámites.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-slate-50 rounded p-4 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 uppercase">Fines estadísticos</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Generación de métricas anónimas para mejorar continuamente los servicios digitales del estado.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Sec 4 y 6 en grid -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">

				<!-- Sec 4: Transferencia -->
				<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.217 10.907a2.25 2.25 0 100 2.186m0-2.186c.18.324.283.696.283 1.093s-.103.77-.283 1.093m0-2.186l9.566-5.314m-9.566 7.5l9.566 5.314m0 0a2.25 2.25 0 103.935 2.186 2.25 2.25 0 00-3.935-2.186zm0-12.814a2.25 2.25 0 103.933-2.185 2.25 2.25 0 00-3.933 2.185z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 font-display uppercase">Transferencia de datos</h2>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
						El Gobierno del Estado de Yucatán <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">no realizará transferencias</strong> de sus datos personales a terceros o dependencias externas, salvo requerimientos de una autoridad competente debidamente fundados y motivados conforme a derecho.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Sec 6: Cambios -->
				<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-6 shadow-sm">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 font-display uppercase">Cambios al aviso</h2>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
						Este aviso puede actualizarse por nuevos ordenamientos legales o mejoras en nuestras plataformas. Cualquier cambio será publicado en este mismo portal. Le recomendamos revisarlo periódicamente.
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>

			<!-- Sec 5: ARCO (full width) -->
			<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-6 shadow-sm mb-6">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
					<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 font-display uppercase">Ejercicio de Derechos ARCO</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Usted tiene derecho de <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">Acceso</strong> a sus datos, solicitar su <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">Rectificación</strong> si son inexactos, pedir su <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">Cancelación</strong> cuando no se utilicen conforme a la ley, y <strong class="text-slate-800 font-bold">Oponerse</strong> a su uso para fines específicos. Para ejercerlos, contáctenos por cualquiera de estos canales:
				</p>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
					<a href="https://www.plataformadetransparencia.org.mx/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex flex-col gap-2 bg-slate-50 rounded p-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-yuc-green/40 transition-colors">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">Plataforma Nacional de Transparencia</p>
						<p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 group-hover:text-yuc-green transition-colors">INAI · INAIP Yucatán →</p>
					</a>
					<a href="mailto:transparencia@yucatan.gob.mx" class="group flex flex-col gap-2 bg-slate-50 rounded p-4 border border-slate-200 hover:border-yuc-green/40 transition-colors">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">Correo Electrónico</p>
						<p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 group-hover:text-yuc-green transition-colors">transparencia@yucatan.gob.mx →</p>
					</a>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 bg-slate-50 rounded p-4 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yuc-green/10 text-yuc-green flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">Presencial</p>
						<p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Unidad de Transparencia, Palacio de Gobierno, Mérida, Yucatán</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Volver -->
			<div class="pt-8 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-slate-200">
				<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-yuc-green transition-colors font-bold group">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
					</svg>
					Volver al inicio
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.yucatan.gob.mx/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors font-bold">
					yucatan.gob.mx →
				</a>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
